## ğŸš€ Usage

```
python3 CSS-nonbinarizer.py
```

This produces:
- Console output showing all c(i,j) and d(i',j)
- Example LaTeX file: example_output.tex
- Visualization images: HX.png, HZ.png, C_gamma.png, D_delta.png

